          JWT → identity/jwt (role: user; algorithms default to RS256 — widen in the emitted policy if the IdP signs with ES256/etc.).
[INFO ] translated    authorization/email-verified
          patternMatching → CEL PDP step (`cel: { expr }`).
[WARN ] skipped       metadata/user-profile
